body:
CL 5005 changes 2 files: mksyscall_windows.go and zsyscall_windows.go (zsyscall_windows.go is auto-generated).

x/sys/windows uses $GOROOT/src/syscall/mksyscall_windows.go directly. And x/sys/windows/zsyscall_windows.go was regenerated by unrelated CL https://go-review.googlesource.com/6320

Alex
